政府表達對僱員對於安全和健康的憂慮，全民共同抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態緊急，如策劃任何工業行動必需經過既定程序。故此是次問卷將於1月31日23:59截止。希望同業們積極參與此調查，讓金總能全面理解金融界僱主於防疫措施現況，以及會員和同業於共同抗疫的意願，以制定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FtoVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=2ce10dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7</a><br />\n<br />\n原post傳送門：<br />\n［行動］［請置頂］全民白絲帶 罷工撐醫護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79e25bd3c37f7f38850b97146a9e8788cbad34a7","tid":1847844,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c0e849d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度簽得七七八八<br />\n麻煩fb tg發出去搵新客源簽"},{"pid":"5c93b234978d11e244cae96a068b670f4bedcace","tid":1847844,"uid":229803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"比大S掃咗一萬個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc773ccacc3cef852a00345209810a7672cf409","tid":1847844,"uid":197364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7160adc3dbc1b6945ba5bc539a9018f93d6dbf09","tid":1847844,"uid":253291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"尋日去左吉祥寺暫時仲充足 今日經過上野都見仲有"},"citedBy":0